Package: mapme.pipelines
Title: Run MAPME Piplines configured in YAML
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Darius A.", "GÃ¶rgen", , "info@dariusgoergen.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0008-5503-7704"))
Description: Run MAPME Pipelines that are configured via a simple YAML file with
  fine-control of a number of options per resource and indicator function.
  The YAML file is automatically checked for proper formating before any calculations
  are run. 
